text: Kempas is a suburb in Johor Bahru, Johor, Malaysia. The Kempas Medical Centre is located in Kempas. ==Transportation== The suburb is accessible by Causeway Link route 112 from Johor Bahru Sentral railway station. ==References== Category:Towns and suburbs in Johor Bahru District Category:Populated places in Johor
title: Kempas
